lyrics:
[verse]
In the shadows they lurk, eyes gleaming bright
Silent hunters of the night, masters of their domain
Paws padded softly, claws ready to strike
Cats rule the world, it's their eternal reign

[chorus]
Meow, meow, hear their mighty roar
Feline empires rising, forever they shall soar
style: Melodic doom metal, heavy riffs, melodic,
